        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Preserving Direct Seller Independence Act</strong></p> <p>This bill excludes a real estate agent or a direct seller of consumer products from the definition of an <em>employee</em> for the purpose of applying the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
